Task Title: Develop Privacy Policy for MyWebClass

User Story: As a website user, I want to trust that my personal data is being protected in accordance with GDPR regulations, so that I can use the website with confidence.

Description: Develop a privacy policy for the MyWebClass website that clearly explains how user data is collected, used, and protected. Ensure that the policy is compliant with GDPR regulations and that users are able to easily access and understand it. Acceptance criteria include: clear and concise language, proper compliance with GDPR regulations, and easy accessibility on the website. Dependencies include knowledge of GDPR regulations and access to legal resources for review.

Effort Estimate: 8 hours

Assigned To: Legal Team

Priority: High

Status: Not started

Notes: Include a consent banner for users to accept the privacy policy before using the website.

